title: Can They Hang?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth, and Mina Kimes debate if the Celtics’ press conference today changed the way they feel about Ime Ukoda’s suspension, if they expect the Dolphins to be able to hang with the Bills this weekend and if they are more concerned about the Packers or Bucs offenses going forward.
